 }}</ref>在這項研究中，被pharmacy checker.com<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.pharmacychecker.com/aboutus/ |title=存档副本 |access-date=2020-12-24 |archive-date=2021-04-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210407170232/https://www.pharmacychecker.com/aboutus/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>核准的國際和美國網路藥房、由美國國家藥房協會的VIPPS（Verified Internet Pharmacy Practice Sites）<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://safemedsonline.org/resource/find-a-certified-vipps-online-pharmacy/ |title=存档副本 |access-date=2020-12-24 |archive-date=2021-01-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210122221049/https://safemedsonline.org/resource/find-a-certified-vipps-online-pharmacy/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>計劃，或是{{link-en|LegitScript|LegitScript}}核准的美國網路藥房、以及經{{link-en|加拿大國際藥房協會|Canadian International Pharmacy Association}}核准的加拿大網路藥房，從前述這幾類被核准藥房所訂購的藥物，經過測試的結果均為真實藥物。從未經認證過的網路藥房所訂購的產品，經測試後被發現有9％是偽藥。<ref name="nber"/>
 
被美國國家藥房協會認可的兩項網路藥房認證計劃中，VIPPS計劃是其中之一（成立於1999年），由美國國家藥房協會本身營運，。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.vipps.info|title=redirect VIPPS|work=vipps.info|accessdate=27 September 2015|archive-date=2010-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101024093632/http://www.vipps.info/|dead-url=no}}</ref>FDA會指引有興趣使用網路藥房的人到VIPPS的網站。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.fda.gov/drugs/resourcesforyou/ucm080588.htm|title=Buying Prescription Medicine Online: A Consumer Safety Guide|work=fda.gov|accessdate=27 September 2015|archive-date=2017-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170518023714/https://www.fda.gov/Drugs/ResourcesForYou/ucm080588.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>另一個計劃是LegitScript，截至2010年9月，LegitScript已為340多家網路藥房提供合規認證，並標示出47,000多家"詭異"的網路藥房。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.legitscript.com|title=Online Pharmacy Reviews & Verification – LegitScript|work=legitscript.com|accessdate=27 September 2015|archive-date=2021-05-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210502051421/https://www.legitscript.com/|dead-url=no}}</ref>在加拿大和所有向美國人出售處方藥的非美國網路藥房，無論他們已有什麼認證，都無法獲得VIPPS和LegitScript計劃的核准。<ref>For VIPPS U.S. only standard see [http://www.nabp.net/programs/accreditation/vipps/standards] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nabp.net/programs/accreditation/vipps/standards |date=20160324213115 }}. For LegitScript's standards see [http://www.legitscript.com/pharmacies/standards] {{Wayback|url=http://www.legitscript.com/pharmacies/standards |date=20141011162108 }}.</ref>
 
===海外網路藥房和美國法律===
透過網路從海外購買藥物進入美國的合法性和風險，取決於所購​​買藥物的特定種類和數量。
 
FDA認為，許多網路藥房受到有組織的犯罪網絡控制，這些藥房不要求處方即出售非法藥物，。<ref name=" http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/websites-selling-illegal-drugs-are-controlled-by-underworld/1/363105.html">{{cite news|url= http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/websites-selling-illegal-drugs-are-controlled-by-underworld/1/363105.html|title= Websites selling illegal drugs are controlled by underworld|work= India Today|date= 22 May 2014|accessdate= 3 November 2014|archive-date= 2018-01-08|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20180108060212/http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/websites-selling-illegal-drugs-are-controlled-by-underworld/1/363105.html|dead-url= no}}</ref>2014年，美國FDA與其他美國聯邦和國際機構，以及如[[Google|Google]]等科技公司合作，對出售藥物給美國消費者的網站採取法律行動。<ref name=" https://www.fda.gov/NewsEvents/Newsroom/PressAnnouncements/ucm398499.htm">{{cite news|url= https://www.fda.gov/NewsEvents/Newsroom/PressAnnouncements/ucm398499.htm|title= FDA targets illegal online pharmacies in globally coordinated action|work= U.S. Food and Drug Administration|date= 22 May 2014|accessdate= 3 November 2014|archive-date= 2015-05-10|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150510041624/http://www.fda.gov/NewsEvents/Newsroom/PressAnnouncements/ucm398499.htm|dead-url= no}}</ref>在美國有數百家合法網路藥房，它們受到美國聯邦法律管轄。<ref name=" https://www.nh.gov/pharmacy/laws/documents/mophcy_laws_rules.pdf">{{cite news|url= https://www.nh.gov/pharmacy/laws/documents/mophcy_laws_rules.pdf|title= N.H. State Laws/Rules Regarding Non-Resident / Mail-Order / Internet Pharmacies|work= New Hampshire Government Website|date= 11 February 2009|accessdate= 14 November 2014|archive-date= 2016-03-27|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160327153852/http://www.nh.gov/pharmacy/laws/documents/mophcy_laws_rules.pdf|dead-url= no}}</ref>
 
FDA認為[[互聯網名稱與數字地址分配機構|互聯網名稱與數字地址分配機構]]（ICANN）應採取更多措施以阻止，還有制裁被視為非法的藥房網站。<ref name=" https://blogs.wsj.com/pharmalot/2014/10/28/icann-or-i-cant-internet-agency-clashes-with-fda-over-online-sites/">{{cite news|url=https://blogs.wsj.com/pharmalot/2014/10/28/icann-or-i-cant-internet-agency-clashes-with-fda-over-online-sites/|title=Icann or I Can't? Internet Agency Clashes with FDA Over Online Sites|work=The Wall Street Journal|date=28 October 2014|accessdate=16 November 2014|archive-date=2020-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200811072232/https://blogs.wsj.com/pharmalot/2014/10/28/icann-or-i-cant-internet-agency-clashes-with-fda-over-online-sites/|dead-url=no}}</ref>ICANN明確表述他們沒有職權去關閉藥房的網站，ICACC在網站上登載一篇說帖："各方對全世界各地網站，何種行為算是構成非法活動有不同的意見時，ICANN並非法院，無權解決這種爭議。" <ref>{{cite web |last1=Serad |first1=Maguy |title=Clarifying ICANN's Role - Online Pharmacies |url=https://www.icann.org/news/blog/clarifying-icann-s-role-online-pharmacies |publisher=International Corporation for Assigned Names and Numbers |accessdate=2 May 2019 |date=August 18, 2014 |archive-date=2020-12-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201201215606/https://www.icann.org/news/blog/clarifying-icann-s-role-online-pharmacies |dead-url=no }}</ref>一個捍衛網路民權的非營利組織[[電子前哨基金會|電子前哨基金會]]認為[[製藥產業|製藥產業]]對互聯網的影響就是一種[[審查制度|審查制度]]，會威脅到美國消費者，影響他們透過網路藥房取得其他國家/地區合法藥品的能力。<ref>{{cite web |last1=Malcolm |first1=Jeremy |title=How Big Pharma's Shadow Regulation Censors the Internet |url=https://www.eff.org/deeplinks/2016/09/how-big-pharmas-shadow-regulation-censors-internet |website=Electronic Frontier Foundation |accessdate=2 May 2019 |date=October 6, 2016 |archive-date=2020-12-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201203051038/https://www.eff.org/deeplinks/2016/09/how-big-pharmas-shadow-regulation-censors-internet |dead-url=no }}</ref>

有項名為“安全進口行動計劃”的提案，建議允許美國各州、藥物批發商、和藥房（而非患者個人）從加拿大網路藥房購買藥物。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.peoplespharmacy.com/articles/is-it-now-legal-to-import-drugs-from-canada/|title=Is It Now Legal To Import Drugs from Canada?|last=Graedon|first=Joe|publisher=The People's Pharmacy|date=1 August 2019|accessdate=13 August 2019|archive-date=2020-08-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200810124759/https://www.peoplespharmacy.com/articles/is-it-now-legal-to-import-drugs-from-canada|dead-url=no}}</ref>

===美國執法行動===
*從海外藥房購買管制藥物屬於違法。從事這種行為的人違反數項處罰嚴厲的聯邦法律。
*[[美國海關和邊境保護局|美國海關和邊境保護局]]可扣押內含處方藥的國際包裹。如果收件人不回應，並且提出他們有權接收這些藥物的證據（例如，有效的處方箋），包裹最終會被退返給寄件人。<ref>See [https://www.fda.gov/downloads/ICECI/ComplianceManuals/RegulatoryProceduresManual/UCM074300.pdf Regulatory Procedures Manual March 2010] {{Wayback|url=https://www.fda.gov/downloads/ICECI/ComplianceManuals/RegulatoryProceduresManual/UCM074300.pdf |date=20180529115433 }} page 9–83 for sample package detention notification letter</ref>實際上，每天裝有處方藥，寄送到美國的的包裹的數量遠超過保護局的檢查能力。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gao.gov/new.items/d04839t.pdf|title=Prescription drugs: Preliminary Observations on Efforts to Enforce the Prohibitions on Personal Importation|publisher=|access-date=2020-12-24|archive-date=2020-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201130020118/https://www.gao.gov/new.items/d04839t.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>在過去即使包裹不是從加拿大寄出或者不符合《[[美國法典|美國法典]]》（第21卷，第844章）的規定也常可通過海關。2006年，一些加拿大藥房報告說，由美國消費者訂購的藥物，有"多達5％"被美國海關查扣。<ref>[https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-2006-mar-01-fi-seize1-story.html " Seized drugs being released"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-2006-mar-01-fi-seize1-story.html |date=20200806090238 }}, ''[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]]'', March 1, 2006</ref>
*除非進口數量龐大（暗示有分銷意圖）或是對公眾健康構成威脅（例如[[鴉片類藥物|鴉片類藥物]]、[[苯丙胺|苯丙胺]]（安非他命）），通常{{link-en|美國輯毒局|Drug Enforcement Administration}}（DEA）和FDA <ref name="Importations of Drugs">{{cite web|url=https://www.fda.gov/ForIndustry/ImportProgram/ucm173751.htm|title=Importations of Drugs|work=fda.gov|accessdate=27 September 2015|archive-date=2019-04-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190423184418/https://www.fda.gov/ForIndustry/ImportProgram/ucm173751.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>不會針對消費者採取行動。
*地方級的執法機構很少會根據藥物進口法律採取行動，但仍會發生。例如在2005年6月，在[[路易斯安那州|路易斯安那州]]的[[巴頓魯治|巴頓魯治]]的當地執法人員逮捕幾名網路藥房客戶，罪名是未有處方卻擁有管制藥物。<ref>[https://www.wafb.com/story/3424884/so-is-buying-prescription-drugs-online-illegal/ "So is buying prescription drugs online illegal?"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.wafb.com/story/3424884/so-is-buying-prescription-drugs-online-illegal/ |date=20200806100903 }}, [[WAFB|WAFB]], June 3, 2005</ref> 
*從海外進口管制藥物的行為違反《美國法典》第21卷，第952章（對於進口非麻醉藥物-第III、IV、或V類藥物，最高可處5年監禁和25萬美元的罰款；對於麻醉藥物和第I和II類藥物，刑罰更重）。沒有處方就擁有管制藥物的行為就違反《美國法典》第21卷，第844章（最高處以一年監禁和1,000美元罰款）。FDA不承認[[電子處方|電子處方]]：FDA認為處方要有效，患者與開立處方者之間必須存在面對面的關係。許多網路藥房認為，確切構成“面對面”關係的主觀定義是如果患者提交病歷記錄要求開立藥物處方，這種行為就可被當作適用治療的附件。法典中第956章和第1301章為攜帶（而非郵寄）少量管制物質進出美國的人，給予免稅待遇。 
*進口未經核准的處方藥（不一定是管制藥物），縱然是作個人用途，也違反法典中第21卷第301（aa）章的規定。<ref name="Importations of Drugs"/>《美國[[聯邦食品、藥品和化妝品法案|聯邦食品、藥品和化妝品法案]]》的確允許進口未經核准的新藥（而沒有已獲核准的美國版本）。但是，這條款不允許進口美國核准藥物的外國製造品。
*法律進一步規定，執法應致力處理對公共衛生構成威脅的個人進口，如果對個人並無不合理的風險時，可酌予允許進口。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.fda.gov/opacom/laws/fdcact/fdcact8.htm|title=Federal Food, Drug, and Cosmetic Act (FD&C Act)|work=fda.gov|accessdate=27 September 2015|archive-date=2009-05-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090512053656/http://www.fda.gov/opacom/laws/fdcact/fdcact8.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>
*進口未經核准的藥物也是違法的（《美國法典》第21卷第331（d）和355（a）章）；但是，FDA的政策是在某些情況下，允許患者保留這些藥物。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.fda.gov/ora/import/traveler_alert.htm|title=Import Program|work=fda.gov|accessdate=27 September 2015|archive-date=2009-05-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090512000625/http://www.fda.gov/ora/import/traveler_alert.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>
