-usd11-billion-2014|title=Healthcare Providers To Spend $1.1 Billion On IT In 2014|work=CRN|date=13 November 2014|accessdate=15 November 2014|archive-date=2014-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141219110713/http://www.crn.in/crn/news/298682/healthcare-providers-spend-usd11-billion-2014|dead-url=no}}</ref>這類技術可幫助該國實現其[[醫療衛生|醫療衛生]]的目標。<ref name="http://www.thehindubusinessline.com/news/healthcare-not-yet-reaching-rural-india/article6599895.ece">{{cite news|url=http://www.thehindubusinessline.com/news/healthcare-not-yet-reaching-rural-india/article6599895.ece|title=Healthcare not yet reaching rural India|date=14 November 2014|work=The Hindu BusinessLine|accessdate=15 November 2014}}</ref><ref name="http://forumblog.org/2014/11/smart-technology-disease-india/">{{cite news|url=http://forumblog.org/2014/11/smart-technology-disease-india/|title=How smart technology can fight disease in India|date=3 November 2014|work=World Economic Forum Blog|accessdate=15 November 2014|archive-date=2014-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141203103550/http://forumblog.org/2014/11/smart-technology-disease-india/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="http://enterpriseinnovation.net/article/bridging-gap-between-urban-and-rural-communities-1317146075">{{cite news|url=http://enterpriseinnovation.net/article/bridging-gap-between-urban-and-rural-communities-1317146075|title=Bridging the gap between urban and rural communities|date=14 November 2014|work=Enterprise Innovation|accessdate=15 November 2014|archive-date=2017-09-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170908024352/https://www.enterpriseinnovation.net/article/bridging-gap-between-urban-and-rural-communities-1317146075|dead-url=no}}</ref> 
 
===印度網路藥房的法律地位===
{{main|{{link-en|印度網路藥房法|Online pharmacy laws in India}}}}

印度並無專門針對網路藥房制定的法律，但有各式的法律間接地管到網路藥房。《{{link-en|1940年藥品和化妝品法案（印度）|Drugs and Cosmetics Act, 1940}}》和《{{link-en|1945年藥品和化妝品法施行細則（印度）|Drugs and Cosmetics Rules (1945)}}》包含有關出售H類和X類藥物的準則，必須持有處方才能取得藥物。細則對於藥物標籤和[[條形碼|條形碼]]也有專門的規定。<ref name=" http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/chennai/state-to-crack-down-on-online-pharmacies/article4663917.ece">{{cite news|url= http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/chennai/state-to-crack-down-on-online-pharmacies/article4663917.ece|title= State to crack down on online pharmacies|work= The Hindu|date= 20 June 2013|accessdate= 3 November 2014|archive-date= 2019-10-04|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20191004010708/https://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/chennai/state-to-crack-down-on-online-pharmacies/article4663917.ece|dead-url= no}}</ref>
 
[[馬哈拉施特拉邦|馬哈拉施特拉邦]]食品藥品監督管理局在2015年搜查位於[[孟買|孟買]]、[[塔那|塔那]]、和[[浦那|浦那]]三個城市的27家網路藥房，並沒收價值200萬盧比的藥物。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.ndtv.com/india-news/chemists-call-for-nationwide-strike-on-october-14-1225190|title=NDTV.com|last=|first=|date=|work=|access-date=|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112024034/https://www.ndtv.com/india-news/chemists-call-for-nationwide-strike-on-october-14-1225190|dead-url=no}}</ref>
 
德里高等法院在公益訴訟（Public Interest Litigation）聽證會上聽過艾哈邁德·扎海爾（Ahmed Zaheer）醫生的證詞之後，於2018年12月12日禁止在印度從事網上銷售藥物的行為。這項命令把透過互聯網銷售藥物的行為視為非法。請願禁止網路藥房的人辯稱，藥物的銷售只能在根據《1940年藥品和化妝品法案（印度）》取得執照的場所進行。網路藥房把藥物送達家庭即違反這項法律。<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.indiatoday.in/technology/news/story/delhi-hc-orders-ban-on-online-sale-of-medicines-in-india-after-doctor-files-plea-1409465-2018-12-14 |title=Delhi HC orders ban on online sale of medicines in India after doctor files plea |date=December 14, 2018 |newspaper=India Today |language=en |access-date=2020-01-07 |archive-date=2020-08-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200806042649/https://www.indiatoday.in/technology/news/story/delhi-hc-orders-ban-on-online-sale-of-medicines-in-india-after-doctor-files-plea-1409465-2018-12-14 |dead-url=no }}</ref>雖然這項禁令到2019年底尚未解除，德里高等法院仍需安排聽證，但是印度的網路藥房業務仍然在擴大之中。<ref>{{cite web
